circumstances:
Crashed in unknown circumstances in Fiskviksætra, Hedmark. All 12 occupants were killed. 
Crew (2./KGr.zbV108):
Olt Hans Liebe,
Uffz Ludwig Holle,
Ofw Fritz Köhler,
Ogefr Otto Lüders,
Gefr Johann Riess.
Passengers:
Siegfried Schlachta, 
Walter Brückner,
Emil Böhnke,
Herbert Kowalowsky,
Lothar Büche,
Ernst Schreiber,
Herbert Stading.
Source & photos: http://ktsorens.tihlde.org/flyvrak/savalen.html
